      "span_text": " the Quitline referral process); 5) providing smoking cessation medications to patients in the ED at the time of discharge (as suggested by others) [CITATION_1] ; and 6) having a designated ED health educator or social worker to provide more intensive cessation counseling and follow-up. EPs also ",
